{"tid":1229520,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"作為醫生連日黎有感","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:40:59.000Z","uid":19725,"like":85,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25b9be6f5427e4cd566e4e4e2ecd4d0a33787252","tid":1229520,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\">借一借用朋友Acc幫手貼文，我係一個小醫生</span><br />\n<br />\n首先，想同連登既手足、巴打、絲打講句加油！<br />\n見到每人都發揮自己所長真係好窩心既感覺。<br />\n例如有一班人係體能上、心靈上都衝唔到，做唔到前線，佢地自發性成立文宣部。<br />\n而佢地既長輩圖，都發揮左好大作用。我有好多都係醫生既朋友都默默咁Airdrop 比地鐵既人<br />\n<br />\n再一次想為前線衝既義士講一聲：尊重！ 你地既行為係成個運動最重要既一環。<br />\n你放心，有好多人係後面Backup 你地！若然再有任何示威活動都靠你地出黎。<br />\n對比起，我地留係First Aid站，好似作為醫生都無咩幫到手。<br />\n<br />\n而我地都好難星期1－5 返工時間參與活動，因為醫院既工作真係好繁忙，係到講聲對唔住。醫生係一個好大既群體，每人都有唔同既agenda，有藍，有黃，有和理，有衝（有醫生同事衝左）。我自己見到既係年輕醫生大多數都有一腔熱誠，但今年都多左年長醫生明白今次示威，並非所有醫生都係醫牲。<br />\n<br />\n我地做到既野就係星期六、日出黎幫手，first aid 物資等等。希望可以係呢個運動做為一個齒輪。教授教過我地 「上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病。」大家已經係香港既「醫生」，醫緊呢個香港！<br />\n<br />\n最後提一提，有咩事都仲可以入黎公立搵我地幫手！我地既使命就係幫市民，唔似警察得把口！但大家都要明白，你地講咩我地可能都要Record down ，我地如果萬一要上庭都要講真話，唔可以講大話。所以你講咩，我地都會信，一定要保護自己！"},{"pid":"87a534f45a607cd0dc9e8e26fd8d4bbcc03d9019","tid":1229520,"uid":23407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:17:23.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a9d87b85e4e50c2dfb732d236fb25dfbf40b1b","tid":1229520,"uid":94834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba770e2ab555e8bb514a5040c189334b2a05c5e","tid":1229520,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a6be76394bebf0d830f5a769a7f68ce627839e","tid":1229520,"uid":22633,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"「上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e2e4def266aec5475627574cdd4ce56838224c","tid":1229520,"uid":60502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"多謝每位無名英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935a072d974ceaaef912b59509b0e845e95d69d1","tid":1229520,"uid":97078,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"孫中山 上醫醫國"},{"pid":"7ebbb4cc8d8763de9540b906c8a0bfa048fd6ab7","tid":1229520,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感動"},{"pid":"a7087986d29a47b65432c4c8856d284886c12a1d","tid":1229520,"uid":182715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a346852f0d5d332500a20e663ea2d5b55a299259","tid":1229520,"uid":260184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d83cb84c3ea2ddafdadfddac8fa2d710504a451e","tid":1229520,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime